      "message": "Line 3323: 🟡 **Iterating all conversations on every new device connection**: `addKnownDevice` calls `getConversations()` and iterates every conversation, calling `isMember` and potentially `connectNode` for each. For accounts with many conversations, this runs on every new TCP link to any peer. Consider filtering conversations by member first (e.g., maintaining a member→conversation index) or at least documenting this as an acceptable cost.",
